Table: NewsDenizen
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-12: [@AdventurerNews]
13-24: Bandit activity
25-36: Activity of named bandit
37-50: Monster encounter
51-64: Monster sighting
65-68: Crime
69-72: Monster attack
