76-78: Humanoid defeat
79-82: Humanoid sighting
83-85: Human disappearance
86-88: Specific criminal's act
89-92: Monster slaying
93-96: Demihuman sighting 
97: Eery sighting
98: Eery activity
99: Demihuman attack
100: Demihuman defeat

Table: AdventurerNews
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d20
1-4: <b>Location Discovery</b>:[@AdventureLocationDiscovery]
5-6: <b>Anomaly discovery</b>:
7: <b>Faction action discovery</b>:
