Table: NewsPolitical
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d16
set: NewsRoll={1d6}
1: Proclamation: alliance
2: Proclamation: banishment/exile
3: Proclamation: bounty offer
4: Proclamation: execution
5-6: Proclamation: feast/festival
7: Proclamation: muster
8: Proclamation: sentence of outlawry
9: Proclamation: tax
10: Proclamation: tournament
11: Proclamation: trial or test
12: Proclamation: visit
13-16: Political scandal involving [|honor|cheating|money|debt|inheritance|position|infidelity|parentage|treason]

Table: NewsDistance
Type:Lookup
1-3: Local
4-6: Area
7-9: Distant
10-14: Very distant

Table: NewsDate
Type:Lookup
1-3: {1d16} days ago
4-6: {1d24} days ago
7: {{1d19}+41} days ago
8: {{6d10}+30} days ago
9-10: {10d18} days ago
11-13: {{1d6}+6} months ago
14: uncertain

Table: NewsNotification
Anomalous [|Dream|Vision|Messenger]
Child 
[|Civic|Military|Political|Religious] representative or agent
First-degree source (brother, wife of informant)
Second-degree source (friend of friend of informant)
Court gossip
Hunter/fisher/miner/woodcutter
Local chatter
Local busybody/gaffer
Message or Letter
Military report
Minor/other NPC
[|Noble|Noble agent|Noble agent]
Participant
Pasquinade or mysterious posting
Survivor or refugee
Named NPC
Witness

Table:NewsVeracity
Type: Lookup
1: True
2-6: Mostly true
7-10: Mix of true and false
11-12: Mostly false
13-14: False
 
