Table:CriminalJobPay
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d10
;crim jobs tend to pay more, but riskier
1: \n Pay: Low ({1d3}*10}) gp./job level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
2-4: \n Pay: Average ({1d3}*100}) gp.job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
5-7: \n Pay: High (500 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
8-9: \n Pay: Munificent (1000 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
10: \n Pay: Munificent (1000 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total], with special reward

