7: \n Pay: Low ({{1d3}*10}) gp./job level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total][|\z|\z|\z|\z|, minor special reward|]
8-9: \n Pay: Average ({{1d3}*100}) gp.job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
10: \n Pay: Average ({{1d3}*100}) gp.job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total][|\z|\z|\z|\z|, average special reward|]
11: \n Pay: High (500 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total][|\z|\z|\z|\z|, valuable special reward|]
12: \n Pay: High (500 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total][@MageSpecialPay] 

