77-89: \n <b>Pay</b>: Average ({{1d3}*100}) gp.job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|total] [@SageSpecialPay]
90-95: \n <b>Pay</b>: High (500 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
96: \n <b>Pay</b>: High (500 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total] [@SageSpecialPay]
97-98: \n <b>Pay</b>: Munificent (1000 gp. job/level) [|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|apiece|total]
