Table:SageSpecialPay
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-04: [@Jewelry]
05: [@MagicItem]
06: [@MagicMiscType]
07-20: [@MagicPotion]
21-30: [@1stMUSpells] scroll
31: [@2ndMUSpells] scroll
32-36: Favor
37-40: Sage will <i>identify</i> item
41-42: Sage offers to trade [@MagicItem]
43-86: Sage offers true, useful lore about some [|item|location|monster|person]
87-96: Sage answers question for free
97-100: Sage does detailed research for free
      
Table:WinterDue
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-65: <b>Due</b>: by spring
66-85: <b>Due</b>: within a month 
86-96: <b>Due</b>: within a week
97-100: <b>Due</b>: as soon as possible 

Table: Rumor
1: \n <b>Rumor</b>: [@RumorDistance] [@RumorDate] \n <b>Topic</b>: [@RumorTopic] [@ConnectionFlag]

Table:RumorDistance
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d20
1-5: Local origin, 
6-14: Area origin, 
15-18: Distant origin, 
20: Very distant origin, 

Table:RumorDate
Type:Lookup
Roll: 1d20
1-3: unknown date
4-10: within the last month
11-15: within the last three months
16-19: within a year
20: more than a year ago

Table:RumorTopic
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-30: Local gossip [@RumorSource]
31-34: [@AdventureLocationRumor], location known to PCs
35-50: [@AdventureLocationRumor], location unknown to PCs
51-54: Local crime [@RumorSource]
55-57: Local criminal [@RumorSource]
58-64: Monster sighting [@RumorSource]
65-69: Demihuman sighting [@RumorSource]
70-74: Humanoid sighting [@RumorSource]
75-79: Missing [|person|goods|animal|item][@RumorSource]
80-84: Monster encounter [@RumorSource]
85-89: Feud between [|individual|faction] and [|individual|faction] [@RumorSource]
90-93: Scandal/secret about [|political|criminal|civic|military|prominent|religious] figure [@RumorSource]
94-96: Treasure location, [@RumorDistance] [@RumorSource]
97-98: Supernatural sighting of [|fey|apparition|ghost|phenomenon|unknown entity] [@RumorSource]
99-100: Supernatural encounter with [|fey|apparition|ghost|phenomenon|unknown entity] [@RumorSource]

Table:AdventureLocationRumor
Type:Lookup
Roll:1d100
;normally an include
01-12: Adventure Location Characteristic: [|Entrance|Hazard|Treasure|Trick|Size|Secret] &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
13-25: Adventure Location Content(s) &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
26-38: Adventure Location Danger(s) &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
