 \n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
65-71: Adventure Location History &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
72-78: Adventure Location Denizen encounter &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
79-86: Adventure Location Denizen sighting &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
87-90: Area Denizen(s) [|General|General|Specific Group|Specific Creature/Entity] &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
91-93: Local Interest/Involvement with Location &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
94-97: A [|recent|recent|old|old|very old] location exploration attempt &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
98: Location Setting Characteristic &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource]
99: Location Setting Denizen(s) &
\n [@AdventureLocationRumorSource] 
100: Location Setting History 

