Table:LowVeracity
Type:Lookup
Roll:1d6
1: [|True|Mostly true]
2-4: Mostly false
5-6: False

Table:AverageVeracity
Type:Lookup
Roll:1d6
1: True
2-3: Mostly true
4-5: Mostly false
6: False

Table:HighVeracity
Type:Lookup
Roll:1d6
1-2: True
3-5: Mostly true
6: [|Mostly false|False]

